headline: Henry Schein Medical Announces Winner of Its 2025 Rising Star Award
summary: MELVILLE, N.Y., April 22, 2025--Henry Schein Medical, the U.S. medical business of Henry Schein, Inc. (Nasdaq: HSIC), announced today that Ian Jeffer, MS, ATC, LAT, Head Athletic Trainer at Desert Ridge High School in Mesa, Arizona, is the winner of the fifth annual Henry Schein Medical Athletics and Schools Rising Star Award. The recognition celebrates emerging athletic trainers with up to five years of experience in the Sports Medicine industry.
